<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="56883" type="habitat">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="56883">Habitat</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="56883">
The species is commonly found in moderately fast flowing creeks and lotic sections of the river (
<bibRefCitation author="Zettel, H." journalOrPublisher="Entomofauna" pageId="0" pageNumber="56883" pagination="225 - 236" refId="B5979656" refString="Zettel, H., 1994. Zwei neue Rhagovelia -Arten aus Mindoro, Philippinen (Heteroptera, Vellidae). Entomofauna 15 (19): 225 - 236" title="Zwei neue Rhagovelia - Arten aus Mindoro, Philippinen (Heteroptera, Vellidae)" volume="15" year="1994">Zettel 1994</bibRefCitation>
), such as in our study.
</paragraph>
